description:
An award-winning Sudoku game that's packed with features including:

* Puzzle of the Day daily challenge - choose your difficulty level, download the puzzle and when completed, compare your time with other players worldwide (requires wifi or cellular data connection). A new puzzle at each difficulty level every day!

* Puzzle Solver - input puzzles from newspapers & books and use all the assistance features to solve them;

* Puzzle Generator - generates literally billions of puzzles at multiple difficulty levels from Beginner through to Diabolical;

* Assistance - various types including manual or automatic pencilmarks; smart hints that help you learn and improve without just giving the answer; and hold & highlight which shows specific numbers or pencilmarks;

* Animated Real-time Background - changes color through the day as you play;

* Choice of Number Styles - different fonts to customize the way your game looks, and choice of pencilmark styles.
